    "title": "Lead Instructional Designer at EduComp Solutions",
    "description": "Join the EduComp Solutions family as a Instructional Designer in Raipur. We believe in empowering our employees with the tools, training, and environment they need to succeed.\n\nAbout EduComp Solutions:\nEduComp Solutions is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Design formative and summative assessments aligned to learning objectives\n• Maintain student records and prepare progress reports\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Utilize technology and digital tools to enhance learning outcomes\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in MS Office\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Pedagogy\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in CBSE/ICSE Standards\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in Bloom's Taxonomy\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with EduComp Solutions!",
